testimony.py - download all bill testimony from the state of Connecticut's
	       general asssembly website.

USAGE

python testimony.py BILL_NUMBER YEAR DEST

     BILL_NUMBER    should be formatted like HB-5303
     YEAR           is the session year
     DEST           is the destination folder

